name: Amirah Al Harbi
profile_summary: The user is a 27-year-old woman who identifies as straight and practices monogamy. She is of Middle Eastern ethnicity with her height being 5'7". Her hometown is Riyadh, Saudi Arabia but she is currently located in Los Angeles, California. She speaks both Arabic and English. Her values are family, career, and religion with a political orientation being moderate. She enjoys cooking, traveling, and fitness in her spare time. She doesn't have children but is aspiring to have them in the future. And though she does not currently have any pets, she is expecting to meet her life partner.
